    <item>
      <title>特朗普，在贸易争吵中谈话，计划在选举后见面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他与加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）进行了交谈，两人将在加拿大举行选举之后开会，这在附近的盟友和主要贸易伙伴之间加剧了关税战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的纳格尔（Nagel）警告对通货膨胀过度乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/ecb-s-nagel-cautions-against-excessive-optimism-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[理事会议员约阿希姆·纳格尔（Joachim Nagel）说，即使该方面的新数据指向正确的方向，欧洲中央银行官员也不会对达到通货膨胀目标有信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/ecb-s-nagel-cautions-against-excessive-optimism-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
